summary: You have cut wood for Belethor all your life and your finally fed up with chopping wood so you decide to go on a rampage.
descriptionHtml:
You have cut wood for Belethor all your life and your finally fed up with chopping wood so you decide to go on a rampage.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This mod includes:

-Craftable Woodcutter's Axe (Able to chop wood)

-Craftable Woodcutter's Axe (Unable to chop wood)

-Craftable Woodcutter's Armor

-Craftable Woodcutter's Gloves

-Craftable Woodcutter's Boots

-Craftable Woodcutter's Helmet

-Craftable Woodcutter's Sword

-Craftable Woodcutter's Dagger

-Craftable Woodcutter's Axe Arrow

-Craftable Woodcutter's Log Arrow

-Craftable Woodcutter's Â Bow

-Craftable Spell Tome: Conjure Woodcutter's Helper

-Craftable Spell Tome: Throwing Axe

-Craftable Spell Tome: Throwing Log
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Spell Tomes for Throwing Axe and Throwing Log are a little broken and they will sometimes crash the game randomly when using them.

The whole point of this mod is to go on a rampage so everything in this mod is extremely over-powered.

If you guys want me to make a more realistic crafting recipes tell me in the comments.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

I am working on making the Throwing Axe and Throwing Log Spell Tomes more stable so they wont crash the game so frequently.
